00:35:05,090 --> 00:35:11,850
♫Oh, my dear dad♫

789
00:35:13,450 --> 00:35:20,250
♫I love that handsome boy♫

790
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:28,430
♫I'm willing to go to Rosa Gate♫

791
00:35:29,640 --> 00:35:34,950
♫And buy a wedding ring♫

792
00:35:34,980 --> 00:35:35,810
Keep the change.

793
00:35:35,810 --> 00:35:43,280
♫Yes, I must go♫

794
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:49,760
♫If you don't agree♫

795
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:06,830
Why hasn't she come out yet?

796
00:36:15,610 --> 00:36:16,510
Where's Siyi?

797
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:21,070
Her grandma said

798
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:23,540
she left by herself early in the morning.

799
00:36:23,550 --> 00:36:24,590
Is something wrong?

800
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:26,140
Would she have left on her own if nothing was wrong?

801
00:36:26,140 --> 00:36:27,020
Full of nonsense.

802
00:36:27,020 --> 00:36:28,380
So she's really angry with us?

803
00:36:28,380 --> 00:36:30,040
You're talking nonsense too.

804
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:31,470
If Wanghe dared to treat me like this,

805
00:36:31,470 --> 00:36:32,270
I'd beat him up too.

806
00:36:32,270 --> 00:36:34,330
I'd give him a flying kick right away.

807
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:37,750
We've waited here for you for ages.

808
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:39,150
Why can't you wait for me?

809
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:41,890
So she's really angry?

810
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:43,230
She really doesn't want us to interfere anymore?

811
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,760
That can't be, right?

812
00:37:05,610 --> 00:37:07,740
It's time to eat after finishing this.

813
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,520
Lao'er.

814
00:37:12,540 --> 00:37:13,390
Let's go.

815
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:14,390
Time to eat.

816
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:24,610
Come on.

817
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:25,400
Give it to me.

818
00:37:25,510 --> 00:37:26,040
Alright.

819
00:37:26,270 --> 00:37:27,140
Here you go.

820
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,800
Peanuts.

821
00:37:34,950 --> 00:37:35,670
Beef.

822
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:42,240
What's wrong?

823
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:44,110
Got bitten again?

824
00:37:45,050 --> 00:37:46,620
That woman.

825
00:37:47,610 --> 00:37:48,670
She bites when she's happy,

826
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:49,770
and when she's not happy,

827
00:37:49,770 --> 00:37:50,570
she bites too.

828
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:51,550
So this time, was it

829
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:53,410
because she was happy or unhappy?

830
00:37:54,770 --> 00:37:55,850
A mix of both.

831
00:37:57,640 --> 00:37:59,840
You can't keep living like this, right?

832
00:38:00,490 --> 00:38:01,880
I've told her a million times.

833
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,940
She just can't break this habit.

834
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:06,220
This time it's not so bad.

835
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,880
Look, it's not even swollen.

836
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:10,040
Last time, it swelled up this big.

837
00:38:10,070 --> 00:38:11,870
Took a whole week to go down.

838
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:13,870
Do you know why?

839
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:14,880
Why?

840
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:16,040
Let me tell you.

841
00:38:16,410 --> 00:38:19,310
Human teeth and dog teeth are both poisonous.

842
00:38:20,260 --> 00:38:20,920
Really?

843
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:21,950
Of course.

844
00:38:22,790 --> 00:38:24,520
Should I get a shot then?

845
00:38:25,310 --> 00:38:26,630
I've heard of rabies vaccine,

846
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:28,850
but I've never heard of the vaccine for crazy people.

